    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. The interior is clean, it drives smooth, and it still has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
