    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain consists of a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a mechanical limited-slip differential for analog power delivery. Key mechanical updates include a documented VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension remains tight, preserving the chassis's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. A well-sorted example with a clean title, optimized for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical health and driving dynamics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
