      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car. This beauty has been such a reliable ride for me, and it's still in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so it\u2019s totally ready for someone new to jump in and enjoy it. Whether you're heading to work or hitting the road for a weekend trip, it won't let you down. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 32500.0,
