    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s spec, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically sound, this example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded poly-bushings, ensuring the chassis handles with the precision expected of the M-badge. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the serious enthusiast.",
